oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 2nd Annual Concert Benefiting the Camp Cambria Classic 2016
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: fund raising; Golf;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (black and red on yellow) announcing the 2nd Annual Concert Benefiting the Camp Cambria Classic 2015 with Steven Tyler, Loving Mary Band, Justin Moore and others on the Lake Shores of Minnetonka July 18. Poster features a metal photoplate of Steve Tyler. Camp Cambria Foundation is an annual golf tournament to raise awareness and proceeds of children with juvenile arthritis.
